---
// Final CTA — bone-led, text-only, hairline-divided. NOT a coral wall
// (that violates "accent at icon scale only" per Black Tomato). Single
// dark CTA, restrained, magazine-finale energy. Hairline dividers
// flanking the headline tie it to the trust-pillar pattern above.
---

<section class="bg-bone text-primary py-28 sm:py-40 border-t border-rule">
  <div class="max-w-[820px] mx-auto px-7 lg:px-0 text-center">
    <span class="block w-12 h-px bg-sun mx-auto mb-12" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <p class="font-label-caps uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-[0.625rem] font-semibold text-primary/55 mb-8">
      The 2027 calendar is open
    </p>
    <h2
      class="font-display font-light leading-[1.0] tracking-[-0.025em] text-balance"
      style="font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw + 1rem, 4.5rem); font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 144, 'SOFT' 30, 'WONK' 0;"
    >
      So, ready
      <span class="italic" style="font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 144, 'SOFT' 60, 'WONK' 1;">
        to sail?
      </span>
    </h2>
    <p class="font-body-lg text-[1.0625rem] lg:text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.65] text-primary/65 mt-8 max-w-xl mx-auto text-balance">
      Hold a cabin for 72 hours, no payment required. Dodie or Clint will reply within 24 hours with the next steps.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-12 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:gap-6">
      <a
        href="/calendar"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center cursor-pointer bg-primary text-bone font-label-caps uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[0.75rem] font-semibold px-9 py-[18px] hover:bg-accent transition-colors focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-accent focus-visible:outline-offset-3"
      >
        Browse Available Weeks
      </a>
      <a
        href="/inquire"
        class="group inline-flex items-center gap-3 font-label-caps uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[0.75rem] font-semibold text-primary border-b border-primary/40 pb-1 hover:text-accent hover:border-accent transition-colors"
      >
        Or send an inquiry
        <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" class="size-3 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M1 8h13M9 3l5 5-5 5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
    <span class="block w-12 h-px bg-sun mx-auto mt-16" aria-hidden="true"></span>
  </div>
</section>
